00:01:15.776 --> 00:01:17.178
<i>Hey.</i>

3
00:01:17.211 --> 00:01:19.580
<i>I fell asleep in front of
the TV waiting for you.</i>

4
00:01:20.914 --> 00:01:22.550
<i>Are you coming home tonight?</i>

5
00:01:23.617 --> 00:01:25.186
<i>Or should I just
go to bed alone?</i>

6
00:01:25.219 --> 00:01:27.588
<i>Do you remember
the noodle stand downtown?</i>

7
00:01:27.621 --> 00:01:29.657
<i>That little street kid
heard us arguing</i>

8
00:01:29.690 --> 00:01:32.193
<i>and he kept trying to sell you
flowers to make up with me?</i>

9
00:01:32.226 --> 00:01:33.527
<i>Yeah.</i>

10
00:01:33.561 --> 00:01:35.496
<i>That boy
went missing a week ago.</i>

11
00:01:37.598 --> 00:01:39.267
<i>I'm leaving the van near there.</i>

12
00:01:39.300 --> 00:01:41.502
<i>Why?</i>

13
00:01:41.535 --> 00:01:44.205
<i>I love you. Navin.
but I have to go.</i>

14
00:01:44.238 --> 00:01:46.106
<i>I haven't
seen you in days. Matia.</i>

15
00:01:46.140 --> 00:01:47.408
<i>Just come home...</i>

16
00:02:38.359 --> 00:02:39.760
